Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.86,0:01:39.20,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:95867,99203}By day she is a happy student\Nat St. Paulia School.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.03,0:01:42.79,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:100038,102790}But at night, she becomes\Nthe phantom thief St. Tail…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.87,0:01:45.16,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:102874,105168}to do good deeds for all who come\Nasking for help from Seira…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.20,0:01:46.71,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:105209,106711}a nun in training.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.92,0:01:52.00,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:107920,112008}Looking to capture the elusive St. Tail\Nis an amateur detective…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.13,0:01:54.09,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:112133,114093}and Meimi's classmate, Asuka Jr.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.09,0:01:56.30,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:115094,116304}As for Meimi…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.38,0:01:59.76,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:116387,119766}she may have more than a bit of\Ninterest in such a determined boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.93,0:02:05.06,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:122935,125063}Meimi's lover is a hedgehog?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.78,0:02:14.94,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:133780,134947}That mom of mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.03,0:02:17.74,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:135031,137742}It's Sunday, and she has to make me\Ngo do the grocery shopping.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.88,0:02:35.59,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:153883,155593}Hey, hold it there!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.98,0:02:52.56,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:170983,172568}What is it?! What's so funny?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.52,0:02:56.69,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:174529,176698}You're a really rude creature!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.98,0:02:57.69,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:176989,177699}Humph!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.50,0:03:12.88,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:191504,192880}I'm leaving!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.46,0:03:19.76,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:198469,199762}Hey, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.06,0:03:29.77,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:206060,209772}If it's the cat, it went that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.93,0:03:30.81,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:209939,210815}Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.06,0:03:34.15,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:212066,214152}Oh, please watch the shop\Nfor a moment!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.40,0:03:36.11,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:214402,216112}What? Hang on a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.19,0:03:37.32,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:216195,217321}Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.40,0:03:41.20,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:220408,221200}Good grief!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.42,0:03:55.75,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:234422,235757}What could this be?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.84,0:04:00.51,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:239844,240511}Y… You!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.47,0:04:03.34,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:241471,243347}You're the rude one\NI met the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.34,0:04:06.05,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:245349,246058}Humph!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.02,0:04:17.90,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:257028,257904}I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.61,0:04:22.07,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:259614,262074}You're all alone, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.53,0:04:27.83,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:265536,267830}Cheer up, cute little hedgehog.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.75,0:04:37.46,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:273753,277465}You're the only person that this\Nhedgehog has warmed up to.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.54,0:04:39.59,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:278549,279592}Really.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.59,0:04:44.18,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:282595,284180}My name is Meimi Haneoka.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.30,0:04:47.01,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:284305,287016}I'll come to see you ever day from\Nnow on! So let's be friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.18,0:04:49.51,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:288184,289519}So cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.31,0:04:53.52,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:291312,293523}Oh, no! I'll be late for school!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.94,0:04:55.65,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:293940,295650}Oh, no! Not again!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.73,0:04:57.02,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:295733,297026}Hey, hold it!\NCome back!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.10,0:04:58.73,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:297109,298736}Don't run away!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.86,0:05:04.86,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:302865,304867}Meimi, want to stop for\Nice cream on the way home?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.03,0:05:08.45,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:305034,308454}There's a new shop that just opened\Nbeside the park on 2nd Avenue.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.28,0:05:11.66,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:309288,311666}Sorry, I've got something to do today.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.74,0:05:12.75,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:311749,312750}Something to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.25,0:05:14.41,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:313251,314418}A date.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.79,0:05:15.58,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:314794,315586}What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.92,0:05:17.33,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:315920,317338}Yup! See you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.34,0:05:23.76,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:322343,323761}A date?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.59,0:05:25.88,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:324595,325888}Good afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.09,0:05:29.72,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:328099,329725}Have you had a nice day?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.27,0:05:34.68,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:332270,334689}Hi! Back again?\NYou're fond of her, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.14,0:05:36.69,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:335147,336691}She's so cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.31,0:05:42.23,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:337316,342238}Why don't you ask your mother and\Nfather if you can buy her as a pet?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.61,0:05:46.07,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:342613,346075}I promise I won't sell her to anyone\Nelse until you get their permission.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.15,0:05:46.86,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:346158,346868}Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.95,0:05:49.41,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:346951,349412}You won't sell her\Nto anyone else until then?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.16,0:05:51.91,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:350162,351914}Sure. I promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.41,0:05:53.79,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:352415,353791}Great!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.08,0:05:56.33,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:354083,356335}Wait for me, my little hedgehog.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.29,0:05:59.33,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:358296,359338}Mister, I'll be back!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.42,0:06:00.46,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:359422,360464}All right, see you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.71,0:06:05.46,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:364719,365469}Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.84,0:06:06.92,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:365845,366929}Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.59,0:06:10.55,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:367597,370558}This hedgehog, sell him to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.93,0:06:13.26,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:371934,373269}But it's already…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.52,0:06:18.56,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:375521,378566}Look, I said I want this hedgehog!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.40,0:06:26.19,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:382403,386198}Please Dad, can I?\NCan I have the hedgehog?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.99,0:06:29.45,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:387992,389452}Did you say hedgehog?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.03,0:06:32.28,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:390036,392288}That's right.\NI even have a name for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.53,0:06:34.91,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:393539,394916}I'll call her Ruby.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.54,0:06:36.45,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:395541,396459}Ruby?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.79,0:06:40.17,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:396792,400171}The ring that dad bought you\Nis a ruby, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.33,0:06:42.13,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:400338,402131}Yes, my engagement ring.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.21,0:06:43.96,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:402214,403966}That's why I named her that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.47,0:06:50.13,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:408471,410139}Hmm… a ruby…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.35,0:06:57.81,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:414352,417813}It does bring back memories\Nof the old days, doesn't it, dear?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.52,0:07:00.39,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:418522,420399}It sure does.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.23,0:07:03.81,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:421233,423819}Eimi, you haven't changed\Na bit since then.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.52,0:07:06.32,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:424528,426322}Why, dear, you haven't either.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.49,0:07:08.28,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:427490,428282}Eimi…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.07,0:07:10.53,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:429075,430534}Genichiro…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.78,0:07:13.57,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:431786,433579}Hello, you two?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.87,0:07:16.29,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:433871,436290}Oh, gee, Meimi, were you there?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.91,0:07:19.16,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:436916,439168}Of course, where else would I be?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.58,0:07:22.33,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:439585,442338}Then it's all right for me to have\Na hedgehog named Ruby?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.67,0:07:23.75,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:442672,443756}Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.46,0:07:25.04,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:444465,445049}Phew…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.84,0:07:28.80,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:446842,448803}It helps, having easy-going parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.09,0:07:34.05,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:453099,454058}Good afternoon!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.64,0:07:35.35,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:454642,455351}What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.60,0:07:38.06,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:456602,458062}I'm really sorry…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.89,0:07:41.19,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:458896,461190}You promised you wouldn't sell her!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.31,0:07:44.86,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:461315,464860}He insisted on buying it.\NHe wouldn't take no for an answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.27,0:07:48.11,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:467279,468114}I'm really sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.58,0:08:01.58,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:479583,481585}Moping will get me nowhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.91,0:08:05.67,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:481919,485673}I'm sure Ruby is having\Na nice life, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.84,0:08:07.46,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:485840,487466}Right! I'm sure of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.51,0:08:14.93,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:493514,494932}"Polar Tear?"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.68,0:08:17.64,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:495683,497643}Yes, it's a beautiful diamond.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.93,0:08:21.77,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:497935,501772}Legend says it's a teardrop\Nof the North Star.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.02,0:08:26.65,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:502023,506652}I shared the diamond with Hayase,\Nan old friend from my school days.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.44,0:08:32.32,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:507445,512324}We took turns, keeping the gem\Nfor two months at a time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.07,0:08:36.24,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:513075,516245}That was our agreement.\NI never expected he would betray me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.66,0:08:38.03,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:516662,518039}He betrayed you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.83,0:08:39.41,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:518831,519415}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.95,0:08:44.25,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:519957,524253}Yesterday was the day I was to receive\Nthe diamond for the next two months.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.67,0:08:50.59,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:525671,530593}Hayase, what are you saying?\NYou haven't given the diamond to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.76,0:08:55.43,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:530760,535431}That's ridiculous, Kamimura.\NOf course I gave you the diamond.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.01,0:09:01.14,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:538017,541145}If you doubt me, search the house!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.27,0:09:05.81,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:544273,545816}Kamimura… maybe…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.02,0:09:12.07,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:548027,552073}You're not trying to keep the\Ndiamond all to yourself, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.69,0:09:13.53,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:552698,553532}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.40,0:09:15.86,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:554408,555868}That's what you're trying to do!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.28,0:09:17.32,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:556285,557328}Cut it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.87,0:09:20.58,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:557870,560581}Do you have any proof that\NI didn't give you the diamond?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.63,0:09:36.84,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:574637,576847}That's the story I heard today.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.38,0:09:40.39,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:577389,580392}They finally called the police\Nand searched the house, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.47,0:09:42.35,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:580476,582353}They couldn't find the diamond.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.35,0:09:47.90,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:583354,587900}And according to the contract,\Nif the Polar Tear is lost…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.98,0:09:51.86,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:587983,591862}the one that loses the gem\Nhas to pay for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.44,0:09:53.32,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:592446,593322}Then…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.07,0:09:57.03,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:595074,597034}On top of stealing the diamond…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.20,0:10:02.66,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:597201,602665}Hayase is holding him\Nliable for the cost.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.41,0:10:09.33,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:603415,609338}I'm really angry! Phantom St. Tail\Nshall retrieve that diamond!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.50,0:10:15.67,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:610506,615678}Is something wrong?\NYou're not usually this touchy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.76,0:10:18.26,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:616762,618264}Seira!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.30,0:10:19.68,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:618305,619682}What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.18,0:10:21.60,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:620182,621600}I went to the pet shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.97,0:10:23.43,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:621976,623435}The pet shop?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.81,0:10:27.02,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:623811,627022}Someone bought my hedgehog!\NShe's gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.31,0:10:31.15,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:627314,631152}I'd even thought up some hedgehog\Nmagic to use on the next caper!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.81,0:10:33.32,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:631819,633320}What's that supposed to be?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.34,0:11:00.80,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:658345,660806}Well then, let us continue\Nfrom line 20.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.43,0:11:07.14,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:665436,667146}Mr. Asuka! Read!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.44,0:11:18.69,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:677448,678699}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.78,0:11:21.99,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:680784,681994}Let's see.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.45,0:11:28.16,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:682453,688167}"Tonight, I'll be at the Hayase\Nmansion to get the Polar Tear"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.25,0:11:29.87,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:688250,689877}"Signed, St. Tail."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.63,0:11:43.09,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:700638,703098}What is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.97,0:11:46.06,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:703974,706060}That's my line!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.68,0:11:48.64,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:707686,708646}Idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.02,0:11:58.07,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:715027,718072}My Lord, forgive me, for I use\Nno gimmick or trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.53,0:12:04.11,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:723535,724119}One!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.08,0:12:07.95,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:727081,727957}Two!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.25,0:12:11.41,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:730251,731418}Three!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.76,0:12:31.14,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:747768,751146}May the blessings of God be with us!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.48,0:12:34.23,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:752481,754233}Meimi, do your best!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.94,0:12:35.69,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:754942,755693}I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.44,0:12:38.65,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:756443,758654}To help me forget\Nmy little hedgehog…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.82,0:12:40.69,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:758821,760698}I'm gonna nail this guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.95,0:12:45.03,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:762950,765035}I don't need your security!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.66,0:12:49.62,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:765661,769623}The police checked it out, but\Nthe Polar Tear is not in this mansion.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.12,0:12:51.58,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:770124,771583}Whatever St. Tail\Nis supposed to be…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.70,0:12:54.16,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:771709,774169}how can she steal something\Nthat isn't here?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.46,0:12:59.50,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:774461,779508}But St. Tail sent me a warning\Nthat she'll show up here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.34,0:13:05.05,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:784346,785055}That's…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.63,0:13:07.64,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:785639,787641}The Mayor's special\Nbadge of investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.97,0:13:10.35,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:787975,790352}I'm staking out\Nyour home, Mr. Hayase.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.69,0:13:22.99,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:798694,802990}The question is where's the diamond?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.90,0:13:26.20,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:804908,806201}That must be Hayase.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.49,0:13:33.37,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:812499,813375}That's…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.04,0:13:37.04,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:814043,817046}But why is my\Nhedgehog Ruby here?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.88,0:13:41.63,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:818881,821633}I must say, this is ingenious.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.80,0:13:46.13,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:821800,826138}No one would ever think that the\NPolar Tear is inside your stomach!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.76,0:13:49.97,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:826764,829975}What a terrible thing to do!\NAbsolutely unforgivable!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.18,0:13:53.47,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:832186,833479}Come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.43,0:13:55.27,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:834438,835272}Oh, it's you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.52,0:13:58.40,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:835522,838400}It's rude of me,\Nbut are you really sure…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.48,0:14:01.15,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:838484,841153}the Polar Tear is\Nnot in the mansion?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.36,0:14:03.69,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:842363,843697}Persistent, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.78,0:14:06.28,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:843781,846283}I told you, I handed the diamond\Nover to Kamimura.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.45,0:14:09.24,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:848452,849244}Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.74,0:14:12.58,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:849745,852581}A hedgehog?\NWhat an unusual pet.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.91,0:14:14.04,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:852915,854041}Don't touch it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.54,0:14:21.63,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:860547,861632}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.71,0:14:22.25,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:861715,862257}Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.30,0:14:32.72,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:871308,872726}It's St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.02,0:14:40.73,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:879024,880734}Darn, you're not getting away!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.77,0:14:43.48,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:881777,883487}My Polar Tear!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.07,0:14:48.07,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:887074,888075}Hang on tight!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.15,0:14:49.07,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:888158,889076}Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.20,0:14:52.95,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:891203,892955}They sure are persistent!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.54,0:14:59.62,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:898544,899628}Look out!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.88,0:15:07.59,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:905884,907594}Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.22,0:15:12.93,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:910222,912933}What the… why are you on my head?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.05,0:15:15.76,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:914059,915769}Don't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.10,0:15:19.56,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:918105,919565}Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.23,0:15:21.90,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:920232,921900}What are you chasing me for?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.98,0:15:23.77,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:921984,923777}Shut up! Stop running away!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.94,0:15:28.74,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:926947,928740}Asuka Jr.! I'm over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.86,0:15:33.12,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:931869,933120}I won't let you get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.16,0:15:36.24,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:933162,936248}You brat!\NWhy are you running away!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.37,0:15:39.08,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:936373,939084}I'm not running away,\NI'm chasing St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.34,0:15:48.80,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:947342,948802}Where are you? St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.92,0:15:50.13,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:948927,950137}Asuka Jr.!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.34,0:15:54.09,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:952347,954099}Hand over that hedgehog!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.76,0:15:58.06,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:954766,958061}You just wait right there!\NI'll get you for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.06,0:16:02.14,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:961064,962149}Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.60,0:16:04.44,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:962608,964443}How hopeless can he be?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.66,0:16:15.53,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:974661,975537}There she is!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.49,0:16:21.37,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:978499,981376}It's showtime!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.10,0:16:45.06,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1003106,1005067}You little pest! Hand it over!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.02,0:16:48.86,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1007027,1008862}Hold that elevator!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.53,0:16:50.40,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1009530,1010405}Shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.91,0:16:59.95,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1017913,1019957}It's no use trying\Nto escape like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.12,0:17:02.50,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1020123,1022501}I'll catch up to you\Nin the other elevator!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.87,0:17:05.54,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1024878,1025546}Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.62,0:17:06.21,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1025629,1026213}What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.96,0:17:09.75,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1027965,1029758}What are you planning to do to her?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.25,0:17:13.72,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1030259,1033720}Shut up! The hedgehog is all…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.72,0:17:26.27,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1042729,1046275}Look this way, St. Tail.\NMaybe I can see her face.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.23,0:17:28.65,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1047234,1048652}I just want to get\Na look at her face.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.73,0:17:29.86,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1048735,1049861}Show your face!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.77,0:17:31.32,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1050779,1051321}How…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.40,0:17:32.03,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1051405,1052030}is…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.11,0:17:33.36,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1052114,1053365}this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.07,0:17:40.83,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1058078,1060831}I'll be getting off here. Bye bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.95,0:17:44.54,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1062958,1064543}Hey! Stop! Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.62,0:17:46.42,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1064626,1066420}Do something, you brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.46,0:17:48.71,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1066461,1068714}Shut up! Stop being a pain!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.83,0:17:53.21,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1068839,1073218}Too bad that elevator doesn't stop\Nuntil it gets to the top!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.09,0:18:02.43,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1079099,1082436}Wait right there!\NI'll get you for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.56,0:18:06.52,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1083562,1086523}I know I should probably\Njust escape now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.81,0:18:08.60,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1087816,1088609}Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.77,0:18:15.82,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1091778,1095824}It really bugs me.\NWhy can't I just let that guy be?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.45,0:18:23.66,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1101455,1103665}Wait, it's coming up?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.95,0:18:28.21,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1103957,1108211}What a stupid phantom,\Nshe's going to follow us up here!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.46,0:18:31.38,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1110464,1111381}Here it comes!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.25,0:18:35.71,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1114259,1115719}St. Tail, we've got you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.96,0:18:37.72,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1115969,1117721}Hand over my hedgehog!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.10,0:18:44.35,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1123101,1124353}What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.18,0:18:50.40,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1127189,1130400}I didn't think I'd get a chance\Nto use my hedgehog magic so soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.15,0:18:52.56,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1131151,1132569}St. Tail?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.36,0:18:55.28,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1133362,1135280}One! Two!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.90,0:18:57.03,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1135906,1137032}Three!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.09,0:19:15.05,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1153090,1155050}Oh, you were able to cough it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.21,0:19:16.34,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1155217,1156343}I'm so glad!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.88,0:19:21.43,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1157886,1161431}That's what you get for being bad\Nand hoarding the gem all to yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.68,0:19:23.76,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1162683,1163767}Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.14,0:19:28.27,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1167145,1168271}Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.31,0:19:32.27,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1171316,1172275}Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.65,0:19:35.69,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1174653,1175696}Goodbye!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.98,0:19:37.73,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1175987,1177739}Take care of the rest for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.28,0:19:42.36,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1181284,1182369}A star?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.87,0:19:55.00,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1192879,1195006}Oh, it's the Polar Tear.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.09,0:19:55.71,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1195090,1195716}Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.84,0:19:58.30,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1195841,1198301}Why did she give this to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.38,0:19:59.46,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1198385,1199469}Hey, son!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.88,0:20:01.63,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1200887,1201638}Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.76,0:20:04.80,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1201763,1204808}Hayase is out cold down there.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.89,0:20:07.47,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1204891,1207477}But I'm arresting him\Non charges offraud.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.22,0:20:11.64,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1208228,1211648}And this is Mr. Kamimura,\Nthe owner of the diamond.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.31,0:20:13.65,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1212315,1213650}I'm so glad…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.77,0:20:17.23,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1214776,1217237}the Polar Tear is safe,\Nthank you so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.32,0:20:18.53,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1217320,1218530}Ah… don't mention it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.11,0:20:22.86,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1220115,1222868}St. Tail, she…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.78,0:20:30.62,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1225787,1230625}Well now, Hayase has been caught.\NWanna come live at my house?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.83,0:20:36.67,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1233837,1236673}Okay! One, two, three!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.50,0:20:41.42,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1239509,1241428}This is to celebrate our friendship!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.17,0:20:44.05,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1242179,1244055}Let's be good friends!
